<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.3">
<l>ilaṉatu vuṭaiyaṉi teṉaniṉai variyava</l>
<l>ṉilaṉiṭai vicumpiṭai yuruviṉa ṉaruviṉaṉ</l>
<l>pulaṉoṭu pulaṉala ṉoḻivilaṉ parantavan</l>
<l>nalaṉuṭai yoruvaṉai naṇukiṉa nāmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is difficult to think as “he is without that, he possesses this”,</l>
<l>on earth [and] in heaven he is with and is without form,</l>
<l>he is not an intellect with senses, he is without end –</l>
<l>we have reached the one who possesses that goodness which is spread.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
